Package org.blockchainnative.ethereum.metadata

Class EthereumContractInfo<TContractType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.ContractInfo<TContractType,EthereumMethodInfo,EthereumEventInfo>
      • org.blockchainnative.ethereum.metadata.EthereumContractInfo<TContractType>
  • public class EthereumContractInfo<TContractType>
extends ContractInfo<TContractType,EthereumMethodInfo,EthereumEventInfo>
    Holds all relevant information about smart contract interfaces in order to allow EthereumContractWrapperGenerator to generate a functioning wrapper class.

    It is recommended to use EthereumContractInfoBuilder to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    EthereumContractWrapperGenerator
